---
import "../styles/wainwrights.css";

import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const WainwrightCount = 92
---

<Layout title="wainwrights">
	<div class="title-bar">
    <h1>Wainwrights</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="about-group">
    <div class="about-text">
      <p>In the 1950s and 60s, Alfred Wainwright wrote his <a class="block-link" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pictorial_Guide_to_the_Lakeland_Fells" target="_blank"><i>Pictorial Guide to the Lakeland Fells</i></a> where he described routes up 214 mountains in the Lake District.</p>
			<p>At the end of 2023 I set myself the goal of climing all 214 of them.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="progress" style=`--_rotation: calc(${(WainwrightCount / 214)} * var(--_total-width));`>
      <div class="inner-progress">{WainwrightCount}<span>/214</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>